{"tid":164904,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同細路傾特首選舉","createTime":"2017-03-21T03:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T03:47:05.000Z","uid":57793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32347f91a7cff1d2fbaebc48cdb96821eabe34a8","tid":164904,"uid":57793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T03:47:05.000Z","msg":"頭先同D細路傾計, 講講下講到特首選舉<br />\n學生A(小四): 我呀婆琴日收到電話，問佢想邊個做特首，佢乜都唔識，是但揀咗林鄭月娥<br />\n我：咁你哋想邊個做？<br />\n學生A：胡官，咁我哋就唔洗做TSA啦，佢反對TSA㗎嘛<br />\n我：學生B你呢？<br />\n學生B(小五)：唔想，一個都唔想<br />\n我：吓？點解呀？點都係佢哋三個其中一個做，始終都要揀一個<br />\n學生B：唓.....都唔到我哋選<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}